name: Womp Rat
Lore: 'Carnivorous rodents. Typically found in Beggar''s Canyon. About the size of an average thermal exhaust port.',
Text: '* Ferocity = destiny. Habitat: exterior planet sites. Ferocity +1 for each other womp rat at same site. Lost if ''bullseyed'' by Luke''s T-16 Skyhopper present.',
